&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; jo ban &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; moti ( english : the drop that became a pearl ) is a 1967 hindi social drama film , produced & directed by v. shantaram on rajkamal kalamandir banner . the film starred jeetendra , mumtaz , akashdeep , vaishali in lead roles and music composed by satish bhatia .